        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Puerto Rico Statehood Admission Act</b></p> <p>This bill establishes a process for the admission of Puerto Rico into the union as a state, on an equal footing with all other states, based on a majority vote of the people of Puerto Rico.</p>  ]]>
        </text>
